title: A.E. Kifisia F.C.
text:
A.E. Kifisia F.C. () is a Greek professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Kifisia">Kifisia</a>, <a href="Athens">Athens</a>, Greece. Founded in 2012 after the merger of A.O. Kifisia and A.O.K. Elpidoforos. They compete in the <a href="Super%20League%20Greece%202">Super League 2</a>, the second tier of <a href="Greek%20football%20league%20system">Greek football</a>.
